---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pro firmy – H2OPE firemní wellness" description="Firemní wellness program na míru pro vaše zaměstnance. Vodíková terapie jako benefity pro zaměstnance.">

  <!-- BANNER -->
  <div class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="cs-only">Pro firmy</span><span class="en-only">For Companies</span></h1>
      <p><span class="cs-only">Firemní wellness program na míru pro vaše zaměstnance.</span><span class="en-only">A tailored corporate wellness program for your employees.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROČ FIREMNÍ WELLNESS -->
  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Benefity</span><span class="en-only">Benefits</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Proč firemní wellness program?</span><span class="en-only">Why a Corporate Wellness Program?</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Investice do zdraví zaměstnanců se vrátí mnohanásobně</span><span class="en-only">Investment in employee health pays back many times over</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
            <span class="benefit-icon">📉</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Snížení absence</span><span class="en-only">Reduced Absenteeism</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Podpora zdraví zaměstnanců vede k menší nemocnosti. Méně prosešlých dní, více výkonu.</span><span class="en-only">Supporting employee health leads to less sick days. Fewer missed days, more performance.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
            <span class="benefit-icon">📈</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Zvýšení produktivity</span><span class="en-only">Increased Productivity</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Vitální zaměstnanci podávají lepší výkon. Energie a soustředění se přímo promítají do výsledků.</span><span class="en-only">Vital employees perform better. Energy and focus directly translate into results.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
            <span class="benefit-icon">🏆</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Employer branding</h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Inovativní benefit odlišující vaši firmu na trhu práce. Přitáhněte a udržte ty nejlepší talenty.</span><span class="en-only">An innovative benefit that sets your company apart in the job market. Attract and retain the best talent.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BALÍČKY -->
  <section class="packages-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Nabídka</span><span class="en-only">Packages</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Jak začít?</span><span class="en-only">How to Start?</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Vyberte balíček, který odpovídá potřebám vaší firmy</span><span class="en-only">Choose the package that suits your company's needs</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="packages-grid">
        <div class="package-card">
          <div class="package-header">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Balíček Start</span><span class="en-only">Starter Package</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Ideální pro první seznámení s vodíkovou terapií</span><span class="en-only">Ideal for first introduction to hydrogen therapy</span></p>
          </div>
          <ul class="package-features">
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Týmový Workshop o vodíkovém wellness</span><span class="en-only">Team Workshop on Hydrogen Wellness</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Každý si vyzkouší inhalaci vodíku</span><span class="en-only">Everyone tries hydrogen inhalation</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Délka 1–2 dny dle velikosti firmy</span><span class="en-only">Duration 1–2 days depending on company size</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-outline-orange package-btn"><span class="cs-only">To Chci</span><span class="en-only">I Want This</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="package-card package-card--featured">
          <div class="package-badge"><span class="cs-only">Nejoblíbenější</span><span class="en-only">Most Popular</span></div>
          <div class="package-header">
            <h3><span class="cs-only">Firemní Wellness</span><span class="en-only">Corporate Wellness</span></h3>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Kompletní program pro dlouhodobý wellbeing zaměstnanců</span><span class="en-only">Complete program for long-term employee wellbeing</span></p>
          </div>
          <ul class="package-features">
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Týmový Workshop o vodíkovém wellness</span><span class="en-only">Team Workshop on Hydrogen Wellness</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Každý si vyzkouší inhalaci vodíku</span><span class="en-only">Everyone tries hydrogen inhalation</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Délka 1–2 dny dle velikosti firmy</span><span class="en-only">Duration 1–2 days depending on company size</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="pkg-check">✓</span>
              <span class="cs-only">Pronájem stroje pro zaměstnance (vodík má opravdový dopad na efektivitu a zdraví zaměstnanců)</span><span class="en-only">Machine rental for employees (hydrogen has a real impact on employee efficiency and health)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange package-btn"><span class="cs-only">To Chci</span><span class="en-only">I Want This</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="packages-note"><span class="cs-only">Ceny jsou individuální dle velikosti firmy a doby trvání programu. Kontaktujte nás pro nezávaznou nabídku.</span><span class="en-only">Prices vary based on company size and program duration. Contact us for a non-binding quote.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="testimonials-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Reference</span><span class="en-only">Reviews</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Zkušenosti klientů</span><span class="en-only">Client Experiences</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Co říkají ti, kteří už vodíkovou terapii vyzkoušeli</span><span class="en-only">What those who've tried hydrogen therapy say</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Po několika týdnech jsem si všiml, že se cítím odpočatější a mám více energie během dne."</span><span class="en-only">"After a few weeks I noticed I feel more rested and have more energy throughout the day."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Klient, 45 let</span><span class="en-only">— Client, 45 years old</span></cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Oceňuji strukturovaný přístup a aplikaci, která mi pomáhá udržet pravidelnost."</span><span class="en-only">"I appreciate the structured approach and the app that helps me stay consistent."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Klientka, 38 let</span><span class="en-only">— Client, 38 years old</span></cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote><span class="cs-only">„Jako sportovec hledám cesty k rychlejší regeneraci. H2OPE mi v tom pomáhá."</span><span class="en-only">"As an athlete I'm always looking for ways to recover faster. H2OPE helps me with that."</span></blockquote>
          <cite><span class="cs-only">— Profesionální sportovec</span><span class="en-only">— Professional Athlete</span></cite>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="testimonials-note"><span class="cs-only">Toto jsou anonymizované zkušenosti klientů. Výsledky se mohou lišit.</span><span class="en-only">These are anonymized client experiences. Results may vary.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><span class="cs-only">Nejste si jistí jak vám vodík pomůže?</span><span class="en-only">Not sure how hydrogen can help you?</span></h2>
      <p><span class="cs-only">Pojďme se spojit na 15 min, kde Vám vše ukážeme a vysvětlíme</span><span class="en-only">Let's connect for 15 min and we'll show and explain everything</span></p>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation</span></a>
      <p class="cta-note"><span class="cs-only">Konzultace je nezávazná. Lidský přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Consultation is free. Human approach.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* WHY */
  .why-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,216,0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,58,92,0.07);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }
  .benefit-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(26,58,92,0.13); }
  .benefit-icon-wrap {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,58,92,0.08), rgba(0,180,216,0.12));
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  }
  .benefit-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
  .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
  .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* VISUAL */
  .visual-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .visual-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .visual-img { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
  .visual-img img { width: 100%; height: 460px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .visual-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .visual-list li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.85rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .v-check {
    width: 26px; height: 26px;
    background: rgba(0,180,216,0.2);
    color: var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* PACKAGES */
  .packages-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .packages-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 860px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .package-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,58,92,0.08);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }
  .package-card--featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,180,216,0.2);
  }
  .package-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--cyan));
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem;
  }
  .package-header { padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); }
  .package-header h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .package-header p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); }
  .package-features { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.85rem; flex: 1; }
  .package-features li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.85rem; font-size: 0.93rem; }
  .pkg-check {
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--cyan));
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .package-btn { margin: 0 2rem 2rem; justify-content: center; }
  .packages-note { text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 2rem; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .visual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .visual-img { order: -1; }
    .visual-img img { height: 260px; }
    .packages-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .benefits-grid { max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
